  "title": "동아대학교 현황",
  "notes": "",
  "bg": "#FFFFFF",
  "html": "<div class=\"shp\" style=\"position:absolute;left:0.0px;top:0.0px;width:112.9px;height:1080.0px;background:rgb(175,85,38)\"></div><div class=\"shp\" style=\"position:absolute;left:21.9px;top:65.3px;width:77.6px;height:388.5px\"><div class=\"tx\" style=\"padding:7.2px 14.4px 7.2px 14.4px;justify-content:flex-start;white-space:nowrap;writing-mode:vertical-rl\"><div class=\"p\" style=\"line-height:1.25\"><span style=\"font-size:26.67px;font-weight:700;color:rgb(255,255,255)\">DONG-A University</span></div></div></div><div class=\"shp\" style=\"position:absolute;left:183.7px;top:147.8px;width:1777.7px;height:295.7px\"><div class=\"tx\" style=\"padding:7.2px 14.4px 7.2px 14.4px;justify-content:flex-start;white-space:normal\"><div class=\"p\" style=\"line-height:1.875;padding-left:54.0px;text-indent:-54.0px\"><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">개    요 </span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">: </span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">부산시 </span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">년재</span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\"> 사립 대학교</span></div><div class=\"p\" style=\"line-height:1.875;padding-left:54.0px;text-indent:-54.0px\"><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">인    원 </span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">: 27,627</span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">명</span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">(</span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">교직원 </span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">1,269</span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">명</span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">대학 </span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">24,057</span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">명</span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">대학원 </span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">2,301</span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">명</span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">)</span></div><div class=\"p\" style=\"line-height:1.875;padding-left:54.0px;text-indent:-54.0px\"><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">선 정 일</span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">: RIS </span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">부산지역혁신플랫폼</span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">(BITS)</span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">에서 부산대학교 총괄</span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">참여대학으로 </span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">RIS </span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">사업 </span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">참여중</span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">.</span></div><div class=\"p\" style=\"line-height:1.875;padding-left:54.0px;text-indent:-54.0px\"><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">주요목표 </span><span style=\"font-size:18.67px\">: </span></div><div class=\"p\" style=\"line-height:1.25\"><span style=\"font-size:21.33px;font-weight:700;color:rgb(192,79,21)\">동아대학교는 부산지역 </span><span style=\"font-size:21.33px;font-weight:700;color:rgb(192,79,21)\">12</span><span style=\"font-size:21.33px;font-weight:700;color:rgb(192,79,21)\">개 대학과 함께하는 원격 교육 지원 위해 가상</span><span style=\"font-size:21.33px;font-weight:700;color:rgb(192,79,21)\">PC</span><span style=\"font-size:21.33px;font-weight:700;color:rgb(192,79,21)\">를 도입하여</span></div><div class=\"p\" style=\"line-height:1.25\"><span style=\"font-size:21.33px;font-weight:700;color:rgb(192,79,21)\">가상</span><span style=\"font-size:21.33px;font-weight:700;color:rgb(192,79,21)\">GPU </span><span style=\"font-size:21.33px;font-weight:700;color:rgb(192,79,21)\">자원으로 설계</span><span style=\"font-size:21.33px;font-weight:700;color:rgb(192,79,21)\">, AI </span><span style=\"font-size:21.33px;font-weight:700;color:rgb(192,79,21)\">모델링 등 다양한 실습을 원격으로 수업할 수 있는 교육 인프라로 활용되고 있습니다</span><span style=\"font-size:21.33px;font-weight:700;color:rgb(192,79,21)\">.</span></div></div></div><div class=\"shp\" style=\"position:absolute;left:170.3px;top:53.4px;width:825.4px;height:72.7px\"><div class=\"tx\" style=\"padding:7.2px 14.4px 7.2px 14.4px;justify-content:flex-start;white-space:normal\"><div class=\"p\" style=\"line-height:1.25\"><span style=\"font-size:32px;font-family:'NanumSquareNeo','A2Z',sans-serif;font-weight:800;color:rgb(28,28,29)\">동아대학교 현황</span></div></div></div><div class=\"shp\" style=\"position:absolute;left:170.3px;top:656.8px;width:623.0px;height:384.0px\"><img src=\"assets/media/image122.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%\"/></div><div class=\"shp\" style=\"position:absolute;left:808.2px;top:609.7px;width:1086.0px;height:397.6px\"><img src=\"assets/media/image123.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%\"/></div>"
